g electronic calls and unplugged shotguns.", "applies_to": ["Light Goose Conservation Order"], "sources": [{"url": "https://www.iowadnr.gov/things-do/hunting-trapping/types-hunting-trapping/migratory-game-bird-hunting", "label": "Iowa DNR — Migratory Game Bird Hunting", "evidence": "Light Goose Conservation Order runs January 24 through May 1, 2027, statewide, with no daily or possession limit."}]}]}